  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765829\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tFirst, a documentary on the history of love in cinema. I say &quot;documentary&quot;, but Love Is All is more of a dream sequence, a 70-minute tumble through screen moments plot <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/exclusively\" target=\"_blank\">exclusively</a> from both real-life footage and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fictional\" target=\"_blank\">fictional</a> movies, all made in the UK, from the 1890s through to last year. So we see couples embracing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/surreptitiously\" target=\"_blank\">surreptitiously</a> on steam trains or hooting with the delight of freedom and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/proximity\" target=\"_blank\">proximity</a> on roller coasters in Blackpool in the 1930s. We see slightly bitter, little educational films warning of the dangers of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/premarital\" target=\"_blank\">premarital</a> sex and some <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/devastatingly\" target=\"_blank\">devastatingly</a> alluring dancing in crashed clubs and halls in each decade of the last century. The director of Love Is All, Kim Longinotto, told me that she wanted the documentary to be about all aspects of love.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t&quot;I always thought all the way through to have a wide <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/interpretation\" target=\"_blank\">interpretation</a> of love because for me, love is love between friends. So you've got the women footballers in 1920 with their arms around each other, celebrating the fact that they're a team. And then you've got this little jam of a film, a little <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/documentary\" target=\"_blank\">documentary</a> film shot in a Norfolk school in 1941, which was this little black girl and you can see she's there because it's to do with the evacuation during 1941 war and she's being made the May queen and she's put on a little <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/throne\" target=\"_blank\">throne</a> and the girls walk around her with flowers and the teacher kisses her on the lips and it's just this most beautiful, beautiful scene.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765829/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p765829\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767033/\">趣味漫画：老外眼里特别找抽的10大行为</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p742101/\">5国语言达人 这10部美剧最适合学英语（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p766962/\">BBC最新纪录片《中国新年》把中国夸上了天</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767096/\">老友记20周年：瑞秋经典穿搭TOP5</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p